name: #3 Circle Of Life - Youth.
description:
SOUND ON!

1/5 pieces from my and his (Dolev Morad) life cycle Dolev is the one that owned what makes your ears jump out during this loop. 
It's the stage of youth.
The youth stages are the stages to stretch boundaries.
Reach the emotional Boundary, and return from it alive!
Adrenaline is what motivates us.
The here and now being important, fun is the keyword.
There is no future and no past!
Let's get started!
